Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:18.12,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}通向月亮的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:24.86,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}君は眠り　夢を解く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:24.86,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你恬然沉睡 梦境已被解开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:30.67,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}誰もいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:30.67,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}无人在此
