Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.66,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}強くなるため
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.66,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}{\frz-90}为了变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:51.49,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}忘れた笑顔 きっと二人なら取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:51.49,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}只要两人努力 一定能找回那遗忘的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.56,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.56,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.43,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.43,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.55,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}今とは違う未来があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.55,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}{\frz-90}即使身处不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.15,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.15,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.21,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}叫び続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.21,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}不停的呼喊着
